To sum and drop cells cells: owned buffer of i32, giving i32.
Let total be 0.
For each index i of cells: total becomes total plus cells at i.
Give total.

To copy then move, giving i32.
Let numbers be array of 4 i32 containing 3, 3, 3, 3.
Let copy be owned buffer copied from numbers.
Give sum and drop cells move copy.

To main, giving i32.
Give copy then move.
